title: WD-40 Multi-Use 330ml Spray Aerosol Can All-Purpose Lubricant, Cleans Rust, for Home & Workshop Use
raw_desc: Ultimate Lubricant in a Spray: WD-40 Multi-Use Product is the original all-round household essential, providing superior lubrication. Protects from Rust and Corrosion: In addition to greasing, it displaces moisture, safeguarding machines and mechanisms. Penetrates and Frees Stuck Parts: Effectively penetrates and lubricates stuck parts or components, making it versatile for various applications. Eliminates Squeaks and Creaks: Say goodbye to annoying squeaks and creaks with WD-40 Multi-Use Product. Multi-Functional Household Essential: An indispensable product that serves various purposes around the house and workshop.
